elements.name: sequenceNumber
elements.description: This is the sequence counter of the QJ records. QJ records are numbered sequentially, beginning with 01.

elements.name: firstFeeClassCode
elements.description: A fee class code. Codes are listed in the AE- Table 6, User Fee Accounting Class Codes, within the Entry Summary Create/Update section of this publication but are not limited only to those.

elements.name: firstFeeAmount
elements.description: The Fee Amount. Two decimal places are implied. If the fee is a whole number, the two low-order (cents) positions contain zeroes.
